    "description": "I like to watch live fighting game videos.<br />\r\nHowever, I dislike playing fighting games.<br />\r\nBecause the stress of losing in a fighting game drives me crazy.<br />\r\nI made this fighting game 【KABENAGURI】 to escape from that stress.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n【KABENAGURI】 is a game in which you punch a wall for one minute.<br />\r\nYou can attack the wall as much as you want.<br />\r\nYou can attack as much as you want.<br />\r\nTake all the stress you usually accumulate and throw it against the wall.<br />\r\nThe damage on the wall will be your score, and you can aim for the top ranking!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn order to bring you closer to the feel of a fighting game, you can use a single attack button for both weak and strong attacks, and there are also command moves that are familiar to players of fighting games.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLet`s KABENAGURI !!",
